#: ../../source/faq.md:124
msgid "在较高版本python环境中安装qteasy"
msgstr "Install Qteasy in a higher version of Python environment"

#: ../../source/faq.md:126
msgid "解决方案是升级到最新的`qteasy`版本。较新版本的`qteasy`已经在`python`3.7 ~ 3.12环境中进行了测试，可以在这些环境中正常运行。"
msgstr ""
"The solution is to upgrade to the latest version of `qteasy`. Newer versions of `qteasy` have been tested in Python 3.7 to 3.12 "
"environments and function correctly in these environments."

#: ../../source/faq.md:132
msgid ""
"较早版本的`qteasy`没有在高版本的`python`环境中进行充分测试，因此存在一些兼容性问题。这样的问题主要存在于v1.1.4及以前的`qteasy`分发版中。"
msgstr ""
"Earlier versions of `qteasy` were not adequately tested in newer versions of `python`, resulting in some compatibility issues. These "
"issues primarily exist in `qteasy` distributions of version 1.1.4 and earlier."

#: ../../source/faq.md:134
msgid ""
"同时，较早版本的`qteasy`在也使用了一些在高版本的`pandas`、`numpy`中即将被弃用的API，这也可能导致对高版本`pandas`、`numpy`的兼容性问题，"
"在v1.1.7及以后版本的`qteasy`中，已经对这些问题进行了修复。"
msgstr ""
"Meanwhile, earlier versions of `qteasy` used some APIs that are about to be deprecated in higher versions of `pandas` and `numpy`, "
"which may have caused compatibility issues with higher versions of `pandas` and `numpy`. These issues have been fixed in versions of "
"`qteasy` from v1.1.7 onwards."

#: ../../source/faq.md:138
msgid "在qteasy.cfg中添加配置信息后，提示数据库连接失败"
msgstr "After adding configuration information to qteasy.cfg, a database connection failure message appears."

#: ../../source/faq.md:140
msgid "有用户反馈，在`qteasy.cfg`文件中配置好数据库连接信息后，仍然提示数据库连接失败。并得到下面类似的错误信息："
msgstr ""
"Some users have reported that even after configuring the database connection information in the `qteasy.cfg` file, they still encounter "
"a database connection failure message, receiving an error similar to the following:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:147
msgid "如果您第一次遇到这样的问题，可能应该首先检查您的`qteasy.cfg`文件。主要检查下面两方面："
msgstr ""
"If this is your first time encountering this problem, you should probably first check your `qteasy.cfg` file. Mainly check the "
"following two aspects:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:149
msgid ""
"配置的key是否错误，`qteasy`稳定版本使用的数据库连接信息配置key是`local_db_host` / `local_db_port` ... 等等，而不是`database_host`，以前"
"在官方文档中曾经存在一些错误，这些错误已经在最新的文档中修正了。"
msgstr ""
"Is the configured key incorrect? The stable version of `qteasy` uses database connection information configuration keys such as "
"`local_db_host` / `local_db_port`, etc., instead of `database_host`. There were some errors in the official documentation before, but "
"these errors have been corrected in the latest documentation."

#: ../../source/faq.md:150
msgid ""
"在文件中给出配置信息的时候，请不要加其他字符，如`\"`, `<`和`>`等等，否则，这些字符也会被认为是`token`或者数据库名的一部份。从而导致连接"
"数据库失败。"
msgstr ""
"When providing configuration information in the file, please do not add other characters such as `\"`, `<`, and `>`, etc. Otherwise, "
"these characters will be interpreted as part of the `token` or database name, causing the database connection to fail."

#: ../../source/faq.md:152
msgid "`qteasy`在解析配置文件的时候，会根据配置的类型，自动转换为正确的格式，例如，数据库端口`3306`应该是`int`变量，直接使用："
msgstr ""
"When parsing configuration files, `qteasy` automatically converts them to the correct format based on the configuration type. For "
"example, the database port `3306` should be an `int` variable, which can be used directly."

#: ../../source/faq.md:158
msgid "即可。`qteasy`会将字符串`3306`转换为`int`型`3306`。·"
msgstr "That's it. `qteasy` will convert the string `3306` to an `int` type `3306`."

#: ../../source/faq.md:160
msgid "下面这个配置文件的例子是正确的："
msgstr "The following configuration file example is correct:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:175
msgid "从数据库中读取数据时，提示建议安装`sqlalchemy`"
msgstr "When reading data from the database, a prompt suggests installing `sqlalchemy`."

#: ../../source/faq.md:177
msgid "有时候，在使用数据库作为数据源，并从数据库中读取数据时，您可能会看到以下提示信息："
msgstr "Sometimes, when using a database as a data source and reading data from the database, you may see the following message:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:182
msgid "以上提示信息建议用户使用`sqlalchemy`."
msgstr "The above message suggests that users use `sqlalchemy`."

#: ../../source/faq.md:184
msgid ""
"总的来说，这是一条`UserWarning`。其实并没有错误发生，数据读取是成功的。出现这条警告信息的原因跟您安装的`pandas`的版本有关。您不需要安装"
"`sqlalchemy`，`qteasy`已经移除了对`sqlalchemy`的依赖. 为了确认为何会出现这条警告，请检查一下您的`pandas`版本."
msgstr ""
"In summary, this is a UserWarning. No error actually occurred; the data read was successful. The reason for this warning message is "
"related to the version of `pandas` you have installed. You do not need to install `sqlalchemy`; `qteasy` has removed the dependency on "
"`sqlalchemy`. To confirm why this warning is appearing, please check your `pandas` version."

#: ../../source/faq.md:192
msgid ""
"如果您使用的`pandas`版本为1.1以上，有可能会出现这条`UserWarning`，但一般来说应该不会影响使用： 这是因为`qteasy`使用`pymysql`作为数据库连"
"接API，但`pandas`从1.1版本以后，逐步开始将`pymysql`的支持去掉了，尽管经过测试，在`pandas`的1.5版本下`qteasy`仍然能够正确读取数据，但是会"
"收到警告信息。"
msgstr ""
"If you are using pandas version 1.1 or higher, you may encounter this UserWarning, but it generally shouldn't affect usage. This is "
"because qteasy uses pymysql as its database connection API, but pandas has gradually removed support for pymysql since version 1.1. "
"Although tests show that qteasy can still read data correctly in pandas version 1.5, you will receive a warning message."

#: ../../source/faq.md:195
msgid ""
"以上问题已经进入了我的修改清单，在接下来的小升级中，会去掉对`pandas`的sql API依赖，直接使用`pymysql`读取数据库，这样就不会出现这条警告信"
"息了。如果您不希望看到这条警告信息，也可以降级`pandas`的版本到`1.1.0`。`qteasy`在开发初期一致固定使用较低版本的`pandas`，绝大部分的稳定"
"性测试基于`pandas`的1.1版本，如果使用1.1版本的`pandas`就不会出现这个提示信息，其他所有功能也都正常。"
msgstr ""
"The above issues are on my modification list. In the upcoming minor upgrade, the dependency on the `pandas` SQL API will be removed, "
"and `pymysql` will be used directly to read the database. This will prevent this warning message from appearing. If you do not want to "
"see this warning message, you can also downgrade the `pandas` version to `1.1.0`. `qteasy` has consistently used a lower version of "
"`pandas` during its early development, and most stability tests are based on `pandas` version 1.1. If you use `pandas` version 1.1, "
"this warning message will not appear, and all other functions will work normally."

#: ../../source/faq.md:199
msgid "从tushare下载数据时提示下载频率过高而失败"
msgstr "Downloading data from tushare failed due to an error message indicating that the download frequency was too high."

#: ../../source/faq.md:201
msgid "某些tushare数据存在每分钟读取频率限制，如果积分不够，下载频率是会被限制的，从而导致某些数据下载不完整，例如下面的情况："
msgstr ""
"Some tushare data has a read frequency limit per minute. If you don't have enough points, the download frequency will be limited, which "
"may result in incomplete downloads of some data, such as the following:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:203
msgid "运行脚本："
msgstr "Run the script:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:209
msgid "出现下列报错："
msgstr "The following error message appeared:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:224
msgid "为此，qteasy设计了专门的重试机制来规避或缓解这个问题。"
msgstr "To address this issue, qteasy has designed a dedicated retry mechanism to circumvent or mitigate it."

#: ../../source/faq.md:226
msgid "您可以尝试修改qteasy的下面几个配置，调整下载数据时的重试次数和延时设置，这几个配置参数是专门为了应对tushare的读取频率限制设置的："
msgstr ""
"You can try modifying the following configurations in qteasy to adjust the number of retries and latency settings when downloading "
"data. These configuration parameters are specifically set to cope with tushare's read frequency limit:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:228
msgid ""
"QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_retry_cnt - 下载数据时失败重试的次数，默认为7次 QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_retry_wait - 第一次下载失败时的等待时长，单位为"
"秒，默认为1秒 QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_backoff - 等待后仍然失败时等待时间的倍增乘数，默认为2倍"
msgstr ""
"QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_retry_cnt - The number of times to retries when downloading data, defaults to 7. QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_retry_wait - "
"The waiting time in seconds after the first download failure, defaults to 1 second. QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_backoff - The multiplier for "
"the waiting time if the download fails again after waiting, defaults to 2."

#: ../../source/faq.md:232
msgid ""
"qteasy在调用所有的tushare函数时，会自动retry，每两次retry之间会逐渐延长间隔。比如，第一次下载不成功时，会暂停一秒重试，如果重试仍然有问"
"题，会等待2秒重试，下一次等待4秒、再等待8秒。。。依此类推，一直到重试次数用光，这时才会raise。"
msgstr ""
"When qteasy calls any tushare function, it automatically retryes, gradually increasing the interval between each retry. For example, if "
"the first download fails, it pauses for one second and retryes. If the retry still fails, it waits two seconds, then four seconds, then "
"eight seconds, and so on, until all retries are used up, at which point it raises."

#: ../../source/faq.md:234
msgid ""
"正常来讲，重试7次后的延时会倍增到32秒，加上前面延时的长度，已经超过1分钟了，正常是不会触发频率错误的，但如果网速过快，或者同时启用的线程"
"太多，可能会有上面的问题。"
msgstr ""
"Normally, the delay after 7 retries will double to 32 seconds. Adding the previous delay, it exceeds 1 minute. Normally, this will not "
"trigger a frequency error. However, if the network speed is too fast or too many threads are running at the same time, the above "
"problem may occur."

#: ../../source/faq.md:236
msgid "这时可以尝试将重试次数改成10次或更多（这样会显著延长下载时间），或者增加等待初始时长："
msgstr ""
"At this point, you can try increasing the number of retries to 10 or more (this will significantly extend the download time), or "
"increase the initial waiting time."

#: ../../source/faq.md:245
msgid "从`tushare`分批下载数据"
msgstr "Download data in batches from `tushare`"

#: ../../source/faq.md:247
msgid ""
"某些时候我们需要分批下载数据，在每批次之间暂停一定时间，例如tushare的某些数据表设置了频率限制，限定每分钟最多下载的次数，如果超过这个次"
"数，会导致下载失败。 这时，我们可以通过下面两个配置参数来实现这样的分批下载和停顿："
msgstr ""
"Sometimes we need to download data in batches, pausing for a certain period between each batch. For example, some data tables on "
"tushare have a frequency limit, limiting the maximum number of downloads per minute; exceeding this limit will cause download failures. "
"In this case, we can achieve such batch downloads and pauses using the following two configuration parameters:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:250
msgid "**`QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_delay`**: 默认值为0，如果设置为一个大于0的整数，表示分批下载时每批的下载数量"
msgstr ""
"**`QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_delay`:** The default value is 0. If set to a positive integer, it represents the number of downloads in each "
"batch when downloading in batches."

#: ../../source/faq.md:251
msgid ""
"**`QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_delay_evy`**': 默认值为0，如果设置为一个大于0的整数，表示两个下载批次之间等待的秒数 以下配置可以使得每下载600组数"
"据就等待一分钟："
msgstr ""
"**`QT_CONFIG.hist_dnld_delay_evy`:** The default value is 0. If set to a positive integer, it represents the number of seconds to wait "
"between two download batches. The following configuration will make it wait one minute after downloading 600 sets of data:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:258
msgid ""
"按照上述方法设置后，每次下载数据时，即使使用并行下载的方式，`qteasy`也不会将所有任务同时提交给进程池，而是分批提交，等待一段时间后，再次"
"提交下一批。"
msgstr ""
"After setting it up as described above, even when using parallel downloading, `qteasy` will not submit all tasks to the process pool at "
"the same time. Instead, it will submit them in batches and wait for a period of time before submitting the next batch."

#: ../../source/faq.md:260
msgid "上述功能是在`qteasy`的`v1.1.11`版本中新增的，如果您的`qteasy`版本较低，请升级至最新版本。"
msgstr ""
"The above features were added in version v1.1.11 of qteasy. If your version of qteasy is lower, please upgrade to the latest version."

#: ../../source/faq.md:264
msgid "如何跑通从数据到回测/优化的最小流程？"
msgstr "How to get the minimum workflow from data to backtesting/optimization working?"

#: ../../source/faq.md:266
msgid ""
"建议按《快速上手指南》中的「一分钟跑通」完成：配置 tushare Token → 下载数据 → 使用内置策略做一次回测。完整链路（配置数据源 → 下载数据 → "
"定义策略并回测 → 参数优化 → 模拟/实盘运行）及对应教程跳转见 [快速上手指南 - 端到端路线图 / 教程](getting_started.md#端到端路线图--教"
"程)。按该路线图中的顺序阅读各教程即可从零走通全流程。"
msgstr ""
"It is recommended to complete the process in one minute as described in the \"Quick Start Guide\": Configure tushare Token → Download "
"data → Perform a backtest using the built-in strategy. For the complete workflow (Configure data source → Download data → Define "
"strategy and backtest → Parameter optimization → Simulated/live run) and corresponding tutorials, please see [Quick Start Guide - End-"
"to-End Roadmap / Tutorial](getting_started.md#End-to-End Roadmap--Tutorial). Following the order of the tutorials in this roadmap will "
"allow you to complete the entire process from scratch."

#: ../../source/faq.md:270
msgid "回测/优化为什么慢？"
msgstr "Why is backtesting/optimization slow?"

#: ../../source/faq.md:272
msgid "可能原因包括："
msgstr "Possible reasons include:"

#: ../../source/faq.md:274
msgid "**数据量与窗口长度**：回测区间越长、资产池越大、策略的 `window_length` 越大，单次回测需要准备与计算的数据越多。"
msgstr ""
"**Data volume and window length:** The longer the backtesting interval, the larger the asset pool, and the larger the strategy's "
"`window_length`, the more data needs to be prepared and calculated for a single backtest."

#: ../../source/faq.md:275
msgid ""
"**参数组数**：优化模式（mode=2）下，参数组合越多，需要执行的单次回测次数越多；已通过多进程并行缓解，但仍与机器核心数及任务规模相关。"
msgstr ""
"**Number of parameter groups**: In optimization mode (mode=2), the more parameter combinations there are, the more times a single "
"backtest needs to be performed; this has been mitigated through multi-process parallelism, but it is still related to the number of "
"machine cores and the scale of the task."

#: ../../source/faq.md:276
msgid ""
"**首次 Numba 编译**：核心回测函数（如 `backtest_step`、`backtest_batch_steps`）使用 Numba JIT，首次运行或参数类型变化时会触发编译，产生"
"一次性延迟；后续同类型回测会复用缓存，速度会明显提升。"
msgstr ""
"**Initial Numba Compilation**: Core backtesting functions (such as `backtest_step` and `backtest_batch_steps`) use Numba JIT. "
"Compilation is triggered on the first run or when the parameter type changes, resulting in a one-time delay. Subsequent backtests of "
"the same type will reuse the cache, which will significantly improve the speed."

#: ../../source/faq.md:277
msgid "**数据准备**：若 DataSource 中数据未提前准备好，回测前会触发数据拉取与窗口装配，也会增加首次运行时间。"
msgstr ""
"**Data Preparation**: If the data in the DataSource is not prepared in advance, data retrieval and window assembly will be triggered "
"before backtesting, which will also increase the first run time."

#: ../../source/faq.md:279
msgid ""
"若需进一步了解回测引擎与性能设计，可参阅 [回测引擎与性能](back_testing/6.%20backtest_engine_and_performance.md) 与《架构与设计》中的 [回"
"测引擎与性能（设计视角）](design/07-backtest-engine-and-performance.md)。"
msgstr ""
"For further information on backtesting engines and performance design, please refer to [Backtesting Engines and Performance]"
"(back_testing/6.%20backtest_engine_and_performance.md) and [Backtesting Engines and Performance (Design Perspective)](design/07-"
"backtest-engine-and-performance.md) in \"Architecture and Design\"."

#: ../../source/faq.md:283
msgid "如何理解「防未来函数」？"
msgstr "How to understand \"future-proof functions\"?"

#: ../../source/faq.md:285
msgid ""
"qteasy 从机制上避免策略在回测中“看到”未来数据：每个时间步运行时，引擎仅向策略注入**该步当时可见**的历史数据窗口，策略在 `realize()` 中通"
"过 `get_data(dtype_id)` 取到的只是该窗口内的数据；在此窗口上计算指标（如 EMA）与实盘“当时仅能看到的历史”一致，因此不会无意中使用未来数"
"据。详细设计理由（为何不做全时间轴向量化、数据窗口如何按步注入等）见《架构与设计》中的 [设计初衷与独特优势](design/08-design-rationale-"
"and-advantages.md)。"
msgstr ""
"Qteasy avoids the strategy from \"seeing\" future data during backtesting by its mechanism: At each time step, the engine only injects "
"a window of historical data that is **visible at that time step** into the strategy. The strategy retrieves only the data within that "
"window using `get_data(dtype_id)` in `realize()`. Metrics calculated on this window (such as EMA) are consistent with the historical "
"data that is \"only visible at that time\" in live trading, thus avoiding unintentional use of future data. For detailed design "
"rationale (why not perform full-time axial quantization, how data windows are injected step-by-step, etc.), see [Design Intent and "
"Unique Advantages](design/08-design-rationale-and-advantages.md) in \"Architecture and Design\"."

#: ../../source/faq.md:289
msgid "use_latest_data_cycle 是什么，如何设置？"
msgstr "What is `use_latest_data_cycle` and how is it set?"

#: ../../source/faq.md:291
msgid ""
"**use_latest_data_cycle**（常简写为 ulc）控制策略所用数据窗口是否包含**当根 K 线**（当前时刻的最新数据）：设为 `True` 时，窗口可含当前 "
"bar（如收盘价），对应“交易时是否允许用当时最新价”；设为 `False` 时，窗口严格为“过去已收盘”的数据。该选择在长期回测中会对收益产生显著影"
"响，qteasy 将其作为可配置项在策略声明与运行配置中暴露。含义与影响见 [设计初衷与独特优势 - use_latest_data_cycle](design/08-design-"
"rationale-and-advantages.md)；具体设置方式见策略类的 `data_types` / `window_length` 声明及 [策略如何声明与使用数据](design/03-data-in-"
"strategies.md)，以及当前版本文档与 API 中的配置说明。"
msgstr ""
"**use_latest_data_cycle** (often abbreviated as ulc) controls whether the data window used by the strategy includes the **current root "
"candlestick** (the latest data at the current moment): When set to `True`, the window can include the current bar (such as the closing "
"price), corresponding to \"whether the latest price at the time is allowed during trading\"; when set to `False`, the window strictly "
"contains data from \"past closing prices\". This choice will have a significant impact on returns in long-term backtesting, and qteasy "
"exposes it as a configurable item in the strategy declaration and runtime configuration. For its meaning and impact, see [Design Intent "
"and Unique Advantages - use_latest_data_cycle](design/08-design-rationale-and-advantages.md); for specific settings, see the "
"`data_types` / `window_length` declarations in the strategy class and [How the Strategy Declares and Uses Data](design/03-data-in-"
"strategies.md), as well as the configuration instructions in the current version documentation and API."
